Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Every missile hit the target!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! Thanks for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.85,0:04:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The target is still operational.\NIt's still heading towards New Tokyo-3.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.48,0:04:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The Air Defense Force doesn't have\Nthe firepower to stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit it with everything we've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.11,0:04:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobilize all of Atsugi and Iruma as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.15,0:04:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hold anything back!\NDestroy the target at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! That was a direct hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The tank battalion's been annihilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Guided missiles and artillery\Nhave no effect either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:05:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good! We'll never get anywhere\Nwith the firepower we've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it an AT field after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Conventional weapons are\Nuseless against Angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. We'll activate it as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to use an N2 mine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but it looks like you won't be\Ngetting a shot at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shock wave approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but my mouth is full of dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.94,0:06:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay. Now then, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.43,0:06:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the hand. I really appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you too, Miss Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just Misato is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.37,0:06:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad we've met at last, Shinji Ikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the target's status?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We're unable to confirm due to\Nall the EMP interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.71,0:06:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw the size of the explosion. It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensors restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got an energy reading\Nat the explosion's epicenter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.51,0:06:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Visual display restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That was our last resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Damned monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,His safety is my top priority,\Nso could you get a car train ready for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.68,0:07:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A direct one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I volunteered to pick him up,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.38,0:07:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'll make sure he gets there. See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.34,0:07:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Man, this sucks! I just had my car restored\Nand it's a total wreck already!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.26,0:07:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}33 more loan payments to go,\Nplus the cost of repairs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.71,0:07:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And look! My best dress has been ruined!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Miss Misato...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.50,0:07:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I was looking and feeling so nice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Misato?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.55,0:07:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you can just take those?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.34,0:07:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an emergency, and we need\Na working car right now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm an international government\Nofficial, after all,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.38,0:07:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,so everything's going to be\Nperfectly fine, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.15,0:07:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think anyone will buy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:08:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no fun. You look cute,\Nbut you're kind of a cold fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, did I upset you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that! You are a boy, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're pretty childish for your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,As we predicted, it's regenerating itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.95,0:08:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If it couldn't, it wouldn't be\Na practical autonomous weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive. It appears it can even upgrade\Nits own operational functions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.29,0:08:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And it seems to have gotten smarter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time before\Nit resumes attacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:46.12,BG,,0,0,0,,The gates are now closing.\NPlease stand clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The special duty organization Nerv?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:48.42,BG,,0,0,0,,Now departing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's a secret organization under\Nthe control of the United Nations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:56.59,BG,,0,0,0,,This is the C-22 Special Express\Ndeparting directly for G33-1.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where my father is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what he does?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:09:02.12,BG,,0,0,0,,This train will bypass all other stations.\NPlease stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My teacher told me his work is vital\Nfor the protection of the human race.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.43,0:09:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,From this point forward, command of this\Noperation will be entrusted to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.76,0:09:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Show us what you're capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.56,0:09:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikari, we will admit that our weapons\Nhave no effect on the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But are you sure you can beat this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what Nerv was created for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hope you're correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The target is still stationary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.91,0:09:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Our intercept system is currently\N7.5% operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, even the UN forces have retired.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I intend to activate Unit 01.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.48,0:09:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 01? But we have no pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a problem. Another spare\Nwill be delivered soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.79,0:09:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you taking me to my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. Did you get\Nan ID card from your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.99,0:10:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:15.13,Signs,,0,0,0,,Come.\NGendo Ikari
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then read this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:19.76,Signs,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Nerv
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.64,0:10:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nerv...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I going to work for them too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.59,0:10:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't have sent me a letter unless\Nhe needed me for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So you don't get along with your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a real Geo-Front!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.22,0:10:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our secret base.\NNerv Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the key to rebuilding our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A fortress for all mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange. Isn't this the right way?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why I hate wearing skirts here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But where the heck did Ritsuko go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.75,0:11:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm just not used to this place yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.29,0:11:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We passed this spot just a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They make these systems\Nto be used, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Would the head of Project E,\NTechnical Department Division 1,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Ritsuko Akagi, Dr. Ritsuko Akagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,please contact Captain Misato Katsuragi\Nof Operations, Division 1, immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.31,0:11:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She got lost again, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.00,0:11:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, hiya, Ritsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.91,0:11:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you doing, Captain Katsuragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.35,0:11:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We're short on both time\Nand manpower, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:11:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. According to the Marduk report,\Nhe's the Third Child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just like his father.\NLike how he's unendearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Their first meeting in over three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice Commander, the target\Nhas started moving again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.05,0:12:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. All personnel, assume\Nbattle stations, Level One.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Repeat. All personnel, assume\Nbattle stations, Level One.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.03,0:12:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare for ground-unit interception.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.54,0:12:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.95,0:12:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds pretty serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how's Unit 01 doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's currently in refrigeration,\Nusing the B-type equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.82,0:12:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it really work?\NIt's never worked before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.82,0:12:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The possibility of activation is 0.000000001%.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We call it, pathetically enough,\Nthe O-9 System.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.83,0:13:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean it doesn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.54,0:13:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't be insulting. It's not zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just a number.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's a bit too late to be saying,\N"Sorry, it didn't work".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.01,0:13:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's completely dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A face? A giant robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't find this in the manual.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is mankind's ultimate\Nmultipurpose decisive weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the synthetic human Evangelion, Unit 01.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Built in absolute secrecy,\Nit is mankind's trump card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this part of what my father's been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:13:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We're moving out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.82,0:14:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving out?! Unit 00's still in\Ncryo-stasis, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.17,0:14:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not planning to use Unit 01?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.10,0:14:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.79,0:14:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on! Rei can't do it yet, can she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.53,0:14:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got no pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,One's just been delivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.28,0:14:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji Ikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.49,0:14:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.45,0:14:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You will pilot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But even Rei Ayanami took seven months\Nto synchronize with her Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for him to do it!\NHe just got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He just has to sit in the seat.\NWe don't expect more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Repelling that Angel is our ultimate priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,To do that, we have no choice but to put\Naboard the Eva whomever has the chance
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to synchronize with it, no matter how slight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you know that, Captain Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.89,0:14:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, why did you send for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:14:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You know exactly why.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:15:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're asking me to take this thing\Nand fight that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.14,0:15:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.92,0:15:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Why are you doing this now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you didn't need me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I called you because I have a need for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Because no one else can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never even seen anything\Nlike this before! I can't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.75,0:15:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be instructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no way I can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't pilot it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to pilot it, do it now\Nand quickly. If not, leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have detected our location.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.88,0:16:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, we don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Get into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I didn't come for this! This isn't fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, just why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't run! Not from your father,\Nand most of all not from yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.10,0:16:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that! But there's no way I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.29,0:16:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuyutsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.63,0:16:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.07,0:16:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we use her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She isn't dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.24,0:16:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.01,0:16:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.05,0:16:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Our spare is unusable. You will do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.27,0:16:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Reconfigure Unit 01's system to Rei,\Nthen re-activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:17:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger. Call off the present work,\Nand begin re-activation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it. I'm not needed after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.40,0:17:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Eva moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.97,0:17:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.04,0:17:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It broke the right arm restraint!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't even have an entry plug inserted!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way it could have moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It reacted without any interface?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.78,0:18:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Or was it protecting...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.24,0:18:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I mustn't run away. I mustn't run away.\NI mustn't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I mustn't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pilot it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Cooling process, completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Right arm re-secured.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Cage contents now in position for docking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.82,0:18:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Signal terminator plug has been ejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger. Inserting entry plug.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:19:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Direct hydro-transmission system,\Nconnection prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.69,0:19:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Plug fixed in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.36,0:19:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,First stage connection initiated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Filling the entry plug.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.89,0:19:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Once your lungs\Nare filled with LCL,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.36,0:19:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,your blood will be oxygenated directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.66,0:19:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel nauseous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop whining! You're a boy, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Connecting main power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All circuits transmitting power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.71,0:19:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Commencing secondary contacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A-10 nerve connection, normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Set the thought configuration to Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All preliminary contacts established.\NPerformance nominal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.74,0:19:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Bi-directional circuits are open.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:20:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Synchronization rate at 41.3%.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Harmonics are all normal.\NNo disturbances identified.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.71,0:20:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.30,0:20:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.76,0:20:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Disengage primary lock bolts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Disengage confirmed.\NDisengaging the umbilical bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Disengage secondary lock bolts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Disengage primary restraints.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise, disengage secondary restraints.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Release safety locks numbers\None through fifteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.08,0:20:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Release confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Currently, Unit 01's condition is free.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.58,0:20:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Internal batteries fully charged.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.35,0:20:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,External battery outlet, normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger. Move Eva Unit 01\Nto the ejector pad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch path is clear. All systems green.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready for launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.89,0:21:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we really do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.01,0:21:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless we defeat the Angels,\Nwe have no future.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.95,0:21:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikari, you're really sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.60,0:21:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.49,0:21:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, don't get killed out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.83,0:22:00.46,Title Cards,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1081.001,710.5)}{\pos(919,696.501)}TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:06.78,Title Cards,,0,0,0,,{\pos(797,50.501)}PREVIEW
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.37,0:23:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva triumphs over the Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.93,0:23:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,However, that was just the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.28,0:23:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji runs away from his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.22,0:23:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Misato's arrogance leads her\Nto try to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Next Evangelion: "Unfamiliar Ceiling"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.09,0:23:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you fan service next time too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.83,0:23:21.14,ED Title Cards,,0,0,0,,{\pos(937.477,718.5)}UNFAMILIAR CEILING
